---
// packages/web/src/components/chains/ChainsIntro.astro
//
// Brief introduction to what Drivechains are.
// Targeted at general users — non-technical language.
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl">
      What are <span class="text-ecash-400">Drivechains</span>?
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-400">
      Drivechains are Bitcoin sidechains enabled by
      <a href="https://bip300.info" class="text-ecash-400 underline decoration-ecash-800 underline-offset-2 hover:text-ecash-300">BIP-300</a>
      (Hashrate Escrows) and
      <a href="https://bip300.info" class="text-ecash-400 underline decoration-ecash-800 underline-offset-2 hover:text-ecash-300">BIP-301</a>
      (Blind Merged Mining). Each chain extends Bitcoin with new
      capabilities — payments, privacy, smart contracts, identity —
      without changing Bitcoin's core protocol.
    </p>

  </div>

  <!-- Three pillars -->
  <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/40 p-6 text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-ecash-800/40 bg-ecash-950/30">
        <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-ecash-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 011.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m9.915-3.374l1.757-1.757a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 001.242 7.244" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Modular Extensions</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Each chain adds a specific capability to Bitcoin.
        Payments, privacy, smart contracts, and more — each
        as a purpose-built sidechain.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/40 p-6 text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-ecash-800/40 bg-ecash-950/30">
        <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-ecash-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Bitcoin Security</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        All Drivechains are secured by Bitcoin's full SHA-256d
        hashrate via merged mining. No new tokens, no separate
        validator sets.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/40 p-6 text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-ecash-800/40 bg-ecash-950/30">
        <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-ecash-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3.75v4.5m0-4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 9m10.5-6v4.5m0-4.5h-4.5m4.5 0L15 9m-10.5 6v4.5m0-4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 15m10.5 0l-5.25 5.25M19.5 15v4.5m0-4.5h-4.5" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Unified Experience</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Sidecoin abstracts chain complexity. You interact with
        a single wallet — the sidechains operate seamlessly
        behind the scenes.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
